data.description: Motivated Seller offering $10000 towards closing costs/repairs/buydown points.Close in Rio Rancho on .5 acres, you'll find this well-appointed home with appx 2235 sf.  This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths and a 2 car garage.   New Septic system and leach field.  Newer roof still under warranty.  New water heater Feb 2023 The large primary bedroom has a full bath, double sinks, walk-in closet and is separate from other bedrooms.   The front living area has a beautiful rock face wood burning fireplace.  The large den has a nice bar and shelving including a pellet stove to keep cozy on those cold nights.  The enclosed porch has a hot tub that overlooks the backyard  and inground  pool.  The finished Studio of appx 400 sf (not included in sf) has electric and AC
